edu.uic.cs.ai1.hw6

Class State

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.uic.cs.ai1.hw6.State

  • public class State
extends java.lang.Object
    Represents a state, either initial or during search. Is itself a node of the search. The state is internally represented as a 4-by-4 array of integers. Provides a State.Direction variable type.
    Since:
    1.8
    Author:
    Marco Mele
